; 25-Jun-91     0.10    (WS) Selwyn removed - now on the disc.
; (Log information missed)
; 01-Apr-92     0.14    (SAH) Fixed position of tilde accents in the bold fonts
; 08-Feb-93             BCockburn; changed GETs to use Hdr: rather than &.Hdr.
